        >
          Notes (
          2
          )
        </summary>
        <ul
          class="mt-2 list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-sm text-surface-700"
        >
          <li>
            Built from publicly available descriptions that the strategy uses a higher timeframe to define overall trend and a lower timeframe to determine entry levels.
          </li>
          <li>
            Daily trend identification and hourly pullback trigger are explicit implementation assumptions added so the idea can compile in FXLab.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
