          class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-surface-500"
        >
          Objective
        </p>
        <p
          class="mt-1 text-sm text-surface-900"
        >
          Single-asset mean reversion strategy for major FX pairs using Bollinger z-score stretch with RSI confirmation and EMA trend blocker
        </p>
      </div>
      <details
        class="mt-3"
        data-testid="ir-metadata-notes"
      >
        <summary
          class="cursor-pointer text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-surface-500"
        >
          Notes (
          3
          )
        </summary>
        <ul
          class="mt-2 list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-sm text-surface-700"
        >
          <li>
            Built from publicly available descriptions of Ernest P. Chan's mean-reverting strategy category.
          </li>
          <li>
            FXLab schema inferred from user-provided examples; field names may need adaptation to exact product schema.
          </li>
          <li>
            Implementation assumptions are explicit where public materials do not provide engine-native details.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
